nodes.text: During the Galactic Civil War, a male Aqualish of the Ualaq sub-species operated as a bounty hunter in the Outer Rim Territories. Clad in a bright orange jacket, he wielded two Model 434 blaster pistols. At some point, while accompanied by two Twi'lek females, he swindled a pair of beings at cards. They promptly drew blasters on him. The bounty hunter had grey skin, with black eyes and brown hair.
